WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.702
Competitive procedures are important because they offer

00:00:02.769 --> 00:00:06.706
Employees opportunities for jobs and advancement.

00:00:06.773 --> 00:00:08.641
They apply to certain promotions,

00:00:08.708 --> 00:00:12.345
reassignments or changes to a lower grade, details,

00:00:12.412 --> 00:00:13.446
or appointments.

00:00:13.513 --> 00:00:18.451
Competitive procedures also apply to training in some circumstances.

00:00:18.518 --> 00:00:22.322
Select each topic to review Article 26 provisions that apply.

00:00:22.389 --> 00:00:25.992
When you're finished, select Next to continue.


